result.name: Hoi Kee Walnut Place

reviews.text: Traditional Chinese "sweet soup", the signature walnut soup particular good!
It's okay to have something sweet here.
If my memory serves me right, this should be the only shop that sell local styled sweet soup in the neighborhood. Fair price, above average food!
Walnut sweet soup is their signature soup! Good to have some crispy walnut placed on the top of the soup
Interesting menu and super efficent place.

result.name: 海記合桃坊甜品

reviews.text: 星期六晚太多人。
材料新鮮份量足，性價比高，地方略為夾小。
土瓜灣近海心廟嘅一間甜品鋪 ，佢都有幾間分店㗎 。有舊式糖水及新式嘅雪花甜品，食物就中規中矩價錢都唔算貴 ，但地區關係呢一間嘅環境及衛生就一般啦！
貴價食品、两碗甜品加4粒湯丸、多謝六十五元！
不過不失 價錢合理 可以接受
